{"tid":669626,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行街見到有人暈低","createTime":"2018-05-18T15:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T15:31:09.000Z","uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fca21562ba311cfa410e8c7980e97378362b5b27","tid":669626,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:19:29.000Z","msg":"頭先係街見到有人暈低左<br />\n有人(疑似醫生)同一班人圍住係度幫手<br />\n都見到有人好熱心咁去搵職員<br />\n雖然我之前有學過下急救<br />\n但係內心掙扎左好耐好唔好衝出去幫手<br />\n知道有醫生係度之後我都係默默咁行開左<br />\n但係依家諗返轉頭好後悔冇行出一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼係幫手報警或者疏散人流都好<br />\n<br />\n總結:希望嗰個人冇事，同埋希望大家如果遇到有事發生都會主動幫手，唔好因為覺得總會有人行出去而猶豫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44dd66f053c1e923743f2758ff12bfc09130c948","tid":669626,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab512aef13a33b2734444187cfa2488d87ee7c8","tid":669626,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"你當初學黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔用不如一早咪學，拎正牌可以覺得總會有人行出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a16b0c8be026aaca33c994a4c46931e2695ba37","tid":669626,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ab512aef13a33b2734444187cfa2488d87ee7c8","tid":669626,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"你當初學黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔用不如一早咪學，拎正牌可以覺得總會有人行出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"當初淆底冇行出去係我柒<br />\n但係我想講嘅係就算咩都唔識都有好多地方可以幫手<br />\n可以幫手報警？疏導人流？搵職員？<br />\n而唔係合理化見到有事發生唔挺身而出<br />\n開post嘅目的就係想講希望大家唔會本着事不關己嘅心態<br />\n而經過呢次經歷，如果真係咁好彩再遇着類似情況，我更加唔會就咁行開去<br />\nNo offence 純粹討論"}]}